      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; solver iterative convergence residuals monitored as proxy.",
      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, formal numerical solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals for continuity and momentum converged to below 1e-5. Factor scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements."
    },
