      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values sourced from device drawings and fluid characterization reports.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model input uncertainty propagation is not required. Nominal values for pump geometry, rotational speed, and fluid properties were taken from calibrated measurement sources. Factor recorded as not-assessed per MRL 2 scope."
