      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; FDA benchmark dataset used as reference experimental corpus.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, assessment of test sample representativeness is not required. The publicly available FDA benchmark experimental dataset provides an adequate reference corpus. Factor recorded as not-assessed per MRL 2 scope."
